data.comment: The first-half is just kicking off.
Hammarby pushes forward through Imad Khalili, whose finish on goal is saved.
In the minute 2, A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
Victor Wolf signals a free kick to Helsingborg in their own half.
Victor Wolf signals a Hammarby throw-in in Helsingborg's half.
In the minute 7, Throw-in for Helsingborg in the half of Hammarby.
Muamer Tankovic (Hammarby) goes for goal but the shot is blocked by an alert defence.
Hammarby have been awarded a corner by Victor Wolf.
In the minute 9, Hammarby's Muamer Tankovic attacks the ball with his head but his effort fails to hit the target.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Stockholm.
Joseph Ceesay for Helsingborg drives towards goal at Tele2 Arena. But the finish is unsuccessful.
In the minute 11, Ball safe as Helsingborg is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Imad Khalili heads in to make it 1-0 at Tele2 Arena.
Great play from Muamer Tankovic to set up the goal.
In the minute 13, Helsingborg to take a throw-in in Hammarby territory.
Corner awarded to Helsingborg.
Helsingborg are pushing forward but Adam Eriksson's finish is wide of the goal.
In the minute 16, Hammarby have a goal kick.
Free kick for Helsingborg in the half of Hammarby.
At Tele2 Arena, Helsingborg are penalized for being offside.
In the minute 19, Hammarby advance rapidly upfield but Victor Wolf blows for offside.
Alexander Kacaniklic gets his shot on target but fails to score for Hammarby.
Hammarby have been awarded a corner by Victor Wolf.
In the minute 21, Aron Johannsson (Hammarby) gets in a strike but the shot is blocked by a defender.
Ball goes out of play for a Helsingborg goal kick.
Throw-in Helsingborg.

Goal kick for Hammarby at Tele2 Arena.
Victor Wolf awards the home team a throw-in.

Free kick Helsingborg.

Hammarby drives forward and Imad Khalili gets in a shot. Without netting, however.
Hammarby awarded a free kick in their own half.

Hammarby are in shooting range from this free kick.

In Stockholm Hammarby drive forward through Imad Khalili. His shot is on target but it's saved.
In the minute 44, Hammarby awarded a free kick in their own half.
Victor Wolf blows to end the first-half.
The second half has started at Tele2 Arena.
In the minute 46, Throw-in high up the field for Helsingborg in Stockholm.

That's a fine assist from Anthony van den Hurk.
